@startuml CU08_Sequence
!include ../_shared/global_style.iuml
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
autonumber "<b>"

title CU-08 — Consultar quizzes disponibles: Diagrama de Secuencia

actor "Estudiante / Público" as Actor
boundary "Angular\nQuizListComponent" as Angular
control "QuizViewSet\n(quiz_viewset.py:12)" as ViewSet
entity "Quiz\n(quiz_model.py:4)" as Model
entity "QuizListSerializer\n(quiz_serializer.py:34)" as ListSerializer
entity "QuizDetailSerializer\n(quiz_serializer.py:42)" as DetailSerializer
database "NeonDB\nPostgreSQL" as DB

== Listar quizzes activos ==

Actor -> Angular : Navegar a lista de quizzes
Angular -> ViewSet : GET /api/v1/quizzes/

ViewSet -> ViewSet : get_permissions() → [AllowAny()]
ViewSet -> ViewSet : get_queryset()\nfilter(is_active=True)
ViewSet -> Model : Quiz.objects.filter(is_active=True)
Model -> DB : SELECT * FROM quiz\nWHERE is_active = True\nORDER BY created_at DESC
DB --> Model : QuerySet
ViewSet -> ListSerializer : QuizListSerializer(queryset, many=True)
ListSerializer --> ViewSet : [{ id, title, course, time_limit_minutes,\nis_active, question_count }, ...]
ViewSet --> Angular : HTTP 200
Angular --> Actor : Mostrar lista de quizzes

== Detalle de un quiz ==

Actor -> Angular : Seleccionar quiz {id}
Angular -> ViewSet : GET /api/v1/quizzes/{id}/

ViewSet -> ViewSet : get_permissions() → [AllowAny()]
ViewSet -> Model : Quiz.objects.get(pk={id})
Model -> DB : SELECT * FROM quiz WHERE pk = {id}\nJOIN question ON question.quiz_id = quiz.id\nJOIN answer_choice ON answer_choice.question_id = question.id
DB --> Model : Quiz with nested data
ViewSet -> DetailSerializer : QuizDetailSerializer(instance)
DetailSerializer --> ViewSet : { id, title, description, course,\ntime_limit_minutes, is_active,\nquestions: [{ id, text, concept_id, order,\nchoices: [{ id, text }] }] }
ViewSet --> Angular : HTTP 200
Angular --> Actor : Renderizar quiz con preguntas y opciones

@enduml
